; Regression test for issue #1045: --explicit --pedantic ignored when options are in file (instead of on command line) (BZ#1045)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1045
; Bug: --pedantic specified as an option directive in the journal file is silently
; ignored, whereas the same option on the command line correctly triggers an error
; for undeclared accounts. The expected behavior is that file-based options should
; be treated the same as command-line options.
--pedantic

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal
             $-10.00  Assets:Cash
              $10.00  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
